own to it ,  there's too much frances mayes in this book .  i thought i liked her ,  but what i really like is her writing style .  it can still be magical - when she gets her ego out of the way .  but when she puts herself front and center ,  she becomes more tedious and pretentious than interesting .  now i'm sorry i read this book ,  because i'm afraid it will spoil my enjoyment of the earlier ones .
